channel.title: Will there be more fx in the future?
channel.description: We already have reverb and delay, I think it would be cool to round out the list of standard fx eventually. Specifically flanger, phaser, chorus. Maybe distortion? But phasers and flangers really are quite fun, what do you guys think?
